(10, 'Silver Luminous Loop Earrings For Him/Her', 'The Silver Luminous Loop Earrings For Him/Her are inspired by the cycles of growth and renewal.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThese silver earrings have a hoop design with rectangular motifs attached to the hoops.\r\n\r\n925 Silver \r\nPerfect for sensitive skin\r\nSize: Height - 3.2 cm, Width - 0.32 cm', 8, 'small,medium', 'earrings', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/ER02111_5.jpg?v=1685630646&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/ER02111_1_1.jpg?v=1685630646&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/ER02111_2_2_2_-min.jpg?v=1686893468&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/ER02111_2.jpg?v=1686893468&width=713', 'Uni', 'Minimal'),
(11, 'Platinum Shiny Crescent Ring', 'Looking for a sign to treat yourself? A ring is the perfect reminder that you deserve all the sparkle in the world.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThis platinum women\'s open ring features one edge with a star motif, the other with a zircon-studded moon motif, and a dangling, zircon-studded star.\r\n\r\nPerfect for sensitive skin\r\nAdjustable size to ensure no fitting issues\r\nRing Diameter: 1.66 cm + Adjustable', 9, 'small,medium,large', 'ring', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R01713_5.jpg?v=1738850225&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R01713_1.jpg?v=1738850225&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R01713_2.jpg?v=1738850225&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R01713_4_c9420723-dbf9-40df-a5e1-a3d9ce6aa2b6.jpg?v=1738850225&width=713', 'Female', 'Minimal'),
