(17, 'Silver Glinting Treasure Bangle', 'The Silver Glinting Treasure Bangle is our favourite new silver jewellery piece! Inspired by the warmth of glinting treasure, it is a statement of classic regality.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThis bangle features oval chained patterns with flower motifs in the centre of each link. This silver bangle is studded with Zircons and is perfect for royalty.', 17, 'small,medium', 'bracelete', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0842_5-min.jpg?v=1720163591&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0842_1-min.jpg?v=1720163591&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0842_2-min.jpg?v=1689859603&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0842_4-min.jpg?v=1689859603&width=713', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
(18, 'Rose Gold Celebration Set', 'This set is meant to complement the bridesmaid\'s look, celebrating her unique style and the joy of her bestie\'s wedding day.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThe rose gold set has a necklace and a pair of earrings which showcases a flower motif set with zircons with a dangling pearl, and it alternates with mango motifs that are connected to the flower motifs.\r\n\r\nPerfect for sensitive skin\r\nEarring Height: 2.5 cm, Width: 0.8 cm \r\nLength of chain: 35 cm + 12 cm Adjustable', 70, 'small,medium,large', 'necklace', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD02274_ER02517_5_80d56a28-7b2b-47ca-9f57-52eea1688a6f.jpg?v=1698384702&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD02274_ER02517_1.jpg?v=1698326621&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD02274_ER02517_2_5b218c65-776a-45cb-9be9-3c22d89083be.jpg?v=1698384702&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD02274_ER02517_4_4.jpg?v=1698384702&width=713', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
