(20, 'Golden Warrior Prince Ring for Him', 'The Golden Warrior Prince Ring is inspired by the courage of warriors. Wear this to bring out your warrior spirit.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThe golden ring for men has an adjustable band with a zircon placed at the centre and embellished lines on the band.\r\n\r\n925 Silver with Gold Plating\r\nPerfect for sensitive skin\r\nAdjustable size to ensure no fitting issues\r\nRing Size Indian 17- Diameter: 1.82cm + Adjustable\r\nRing Size Indian 20- Diameter: 1.91cm + Adjustable', 15, 'small,medium', 'ring', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R02088-17_5.jpg?v=1741328656&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R02088-17_1.jpg?v=1741328656&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R02088-17_2.jpg?v=1741328656&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/R02088-20_4_401814f6-3a29-4711-ba81-f84aac93f6e7.jpg?v=1741328656&width=713', 'Male', 'Wedding'),
(21, 'Starlight Gold Necklace', 'Golden petals, a soft cascade, Whispers of beauty, forever made. Unfurl a cascade of elegance with the Cascata Gold Necklace. Delicate red floral motifs dance across your neckline, a captivating prelude to the symphony of geometric designs below. Each layer unfolds with a unique charm, culminating in a vibrant red and white stone flower. Delicate white pearl and red bead hangings whisper of timeless beauty, catching the light with every move', 110.5, 'small,medium', 'necklace', 'https://s7ap1.scene7.com/is/image/noveljewelsprod/JTXYA20-AENC009%281%29', 'images/p21_2.png', 'images/p21_3.png', 'images/p21_4.png', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
(22, 'Gaja Gamini Gold Choker', 'A caress of gold, whispering tales of eternal love wrapped gracefully around your neck! The majestic elephant motifs of this ornate choker are masterfully crafted to create the most beautiful symphony with floral patterns. Created in 22 karat gold with antique finish, this choker will be hard to part from. They say elephants are the memory keepers of the world and once you wear this choker, you will never part with the memory of it!', 115, 'small,medium', 'necklace', 'https://s7ap1.scene7.com/is/image/noveljewelsprod/GTAYA80-ACNC186%281%29', 'images/p22_2.png', 'images/p22_3.png', 'images/p22_4.png', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
(23, 'Mohini Gold Choker', 'There are necklaces that belong to you. Then there are necklaces that you belong to. With all your heart! A majestic choker crafted in 22 karat gold that sparkles in a sophisticated antique finish. Embellished with stones, this heavy occasion wear necklace is a testament to traditional craftsmanship and expert artistry. You will feel the pull of this sublime piece long after you have taken it off!', 120, 'medium,large', 'necklace', 'images/p23_1.png', 'https://s7ap1.scene7.com/is/image/noveljewelsprod/JTAYA10-AANC489%281%29', 'images/p23_3.png', 'images/p23_4.png', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
(24, 'Golden Wedding Knot Mangalsutra', 'The promises you made during the wedding are symbolised in this mangalsutra. Gift this as a surprise for your significant other!\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThis golden mangalsutra features an entwined charm with black beads.\r\n\r\nPerfect for sensitive skin\r\nLength of chain: 44 cm + 5 cm Adjustable\r\nMotif Height: 1 cm, Width: 3 cm ', 14, 'small,medium,large', 'necklace', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD01943_5.jpg?v=1713439457&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD01943_1.jpg?v=1713439457&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD01943_2.jpg?v=1713439457&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/PD01943_4_36e65b5f-5ff7-4325-b50b-271343d02442.jpg?v=1713441429&width=713', 'Female', 'Wedding'),
(25, 'Rose Gold Protected Love Mangalsutra Bracelet', 'The Rose Gold Protected Love Mangalsutra Bracelet is inspired by the love that is kept secret to safeguard it against negative energies.\r\n\r\nThe Design:\r\nThe rose gold bracelet has a round charm at the centre with zircons embedded on the rim.\r\nAdjustable size to ensure no fitting issues\r\nAAA+ Quality Zircons\r\nLength of the bracelet is 17 cm and 3 cm adjustable chain\r\nCharm: 1 cm x 1.8 cm', 12, 'small,large', 'bracelete', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0409_5.jpg?v=1694154728&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0409_1.jpg?v=1694154728&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0409_2.jpg?v=1694154728&width=713', 'https://www.giva.co/cdn/shop/files/BR0409_4.jpg?v=1694154727&width=713', 'Female', 'Minimal'),
